OL,3,CPeople with learning disabilities
OL,4,Cmodernise 'outdated' records at Kresen
OL,5,CKernow
OL,7,FEight people with learning
OL,8,Fdisabilities have been updating
OL,9,Frecords to reflect modern attitudes at
OL,10,Fan exhibition being held in Cornwall.
OL,12,FKresen Kernow is home to the Duchy's
OL,13,Fbiggest collection of historical
OL,14,Frecords but a new pop-up exhibition
OL,15,Fhas been redressing some of the
OL,16,Foutdated perspectives.
OL,18,FEbony-Rose Thomas, one of the
OL,19,Fcontributors, says the language in
OL,20,Fsome of the historical records is very
OL,21,Foffensive.
