OL,7,F"It really did make me cry because
OL,8,Fwe're not retarded", she said.
OL,10,F"We're not crippled. We're normal
OL,11,Fhumans. We bleed the same blood as
OL,12,Feverybody else", Ebony-Rose added.
OL,14,F"We should be respected like that. We
OL,15,Fshouldn't treated differently because
OL,16,Fwe're disabled. We should be part of
OL,17,Fthe community and part of like, the
OL,18,Fsociety."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
