OL,7,FMany of those who contributed said
OL,8,Fthey were very "proud" to be part of
OL,9,Fthe exhibition.
OL,11,FRory said: "I like my Cornish Heritage
OL,12,Fbecause I was born in Cornwall. And
OL,13,Fall of those things helped me become a
OL,14,FCornishman."
OL,16,FTamsin Mallet, the Collections
OL,17,FManager, said it is important for
OL,18,FKresen Kernow to always keep updating
OL,19,Fits records because much of the older
OL,20,Fcollection does not share the same
OL,21,Fvalues we have today.
