OL,7,FMarie Whitehurst from disAbility
OL,8,FCornwall, who helped facilitate the
OL,9,Fexhibition, says people in Cornwall
OL,10,Ftoday do still have a hard time in
OL,11,Fmodern society.
OL,13,FMarie said: "Some of the stories that
OL,14,Fthey shared is the fact that they've
OL,15,Fbeen made fun of. Their experiences
OL,16,Fmean they've ended up in hospital, in
OL,17,Fprison, and that shouldn't be
OL,18,Fhappening.
