OL,7,F"We need to make sure that that
OL,8,Fsupport out that for people with a
OL,9,Flearning disability."
OL,11,FMaking the exhibit itself accessible
OL,12,Fwas extremely important, so visitors
OL,13,Fcan watch video interviews signed in
OL,14,FMakaton, as well as picking up easy
OL,15,Fread pamphlets about the contributors.
OL,17,FThe exhibition remains on display
OL,18,Funtil the end of January, but it will
OL,19,Fbe recorded permanently in the Cornish
OL,20,Farchives as the latest addition to the
OL,21,FKresen Kernow records.
